headline: 3 Reasons LEN is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Lennar currently trades at $115.10 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a middling return of 3.5%. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 13% gain during that period.
